Steps for a new task:

1 git fetch origin main:main
2 git checkout main
3 git branch -D old_branch
4 git checkout -b new_branch
5 git branch -D main

At this moment we are starting our work:

1 git add .
2 git status
3 git commit -m "Some comments related your changes"
4 git push origin new_branch

Move to https://github.com:

1 Click Create Pull Request main <- new_branch
2 Click Merge Pull Request
3 Click Confirm merge
